                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1904574/">浮城°GnaIjniX</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-07-10</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">大师作品，推荐阅读。翻译的也好。语言真魅力。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="708673468">
